  "detailed_description": "<h1>Feature List</h1><p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore more than 20+ relaxing chapters filled with hidden object scenes and minigames. </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover over 70 unique hidden object scenes and engaging minigames. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy soothing, gentle music throughout your gameplay. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expand and decorate your garden with a variety of new plants and flowers. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover stunning, handcrafted nature scenes from around the globe.</p></li></ul></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the serene and tranquil world of Nature Escapes 3, the latest installment in the beloved hidden object game series. Immerse yourself in the beauty of nature as you journey through 24 all-new chapters, each filled with handcrafted landscapes that bring the natural world to life. With an enhanced selection of plants and decorations, you can now create your own garden sanctuary, making the game experience even more personal and soothing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383050/extras/b5262eb24880007d0e95d9d80d15e740.poster.avif?t=1729642198\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383050/extras/b5262eb24880007d0e95d9d80d15e740.webm?t=1729642198\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383050/extras/b5262eb24880007d0e95d9d80d15e740.mp4?t=1729642198\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nature Escapes 3 continues the tradition of offering gentle, relaxing gameplay accompanied by soothing music, perfect for unwinding after a long day. Whether you’re a seasoned player or new to the series, you'll find joy in uncovering hidden treasures across a variety of peaceful settings. The expanded content offers more levels, more plants, and even more serene scenes, making it the ideal escape into nature’s embrace.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383050/extras/3e887c15ea8e20e488f78b8a8f2f705c.poster.avif?t=1729642198\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383050/extras/3e887c15ea8e20e488f78b8a8f2f705c.webm?t=1729642198\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383050/extras/3e887c15ea8e20e488f78b8a8f2f705c.mp4?t=1729642198\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383050/extras/8fa9c351ff5d4cb299389295983d1438.poster.avif?t=1729642198\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383050/extras/8fa9c351ff5d4cb299389295983d1438.webm?t=1729642198\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383050/extras/8fa9c351ff5d4cb299389295983d1438.mp4?t=1729642198\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy the tranquility of nature from the comfort of your home with Nature Escapes 3, where you can craft your dream garden and immerse yourself in nature all in one place.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the serene and tranquil world of Nature Escapes 3, the latest installment in the beloved hidden object game series. Immerse yourself in the beauty of nature as you journey through 24 all-new chapters, each filled with handcrafted landscapes that bring the natural world to life. With an enhanced selection of plants and decorations, you can now create your own garden sanctuary, making the game experience even more personal and soothing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383050/extras/b5262eb24880007d0e95d9d80d15e740.poster.avif?t=1729642198\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383050/extras/b5262eb24880007d0e95d9d80d15e740.webm?t=1729642198\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383050/extras/b5262eb24880007d0e95d9d80d15e740.mp4?t=1729642198\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nature Escapes 3 continues the tradition of offering gentle, relaxing gameplay accompanied by soothing music, perfect for unwinding after a long day. Whether you’re a seasoned player or new to the series, you'll find joy in uncovering hidden treasures across a variety of peaceful settings. The expanded content offers more levels, more plants, and even more serene scenes, making it the ideal escape into nature’s embrace.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383050/extras/3e887c15ea8e20e488f78b8a8f2f705c.poster.avif?t=1729642198\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383050/extras/3e887c15ea8e20e488f78b8a8f2f705c.webm?t=1729642198\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383050/extras/3e887c15ea8e20e488f78b8a8f2f705c.mp4?t=1729642198\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383050/extras/8fa9c351ff5d4cb299389295983d1438.poster.avif?t=1729642198\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383050/extras/8fa9c351ff5d4cb299389295983d1438.webm?t=1729642198\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383050/extras/8fa9c351ff5d4cb299389295983d1438.mp4?t=1729642198\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy the tranquility of nature from the comfort of your home with Nature Escapes 3, where you can craft your dream garden and immerse yourself in nature all in one place.</p>",
